Package: SpaceMosaic
Title: Spatially-Resolved Differential Expression via Elliptical Patch Partitions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Patrick", "Danaher", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "patrick.danaher@bruker.com")
Description: Partitions spatial transcriptomics tissue into elliptical patches
    that maximize within-patch design variable variance, then performs
    per-patch differential expression with Bayesian meta-analysis and
    spatial subgroup detection.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
